=3D"Edit section: Minor League Baseball"><span>edit</span></a><span class=
=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The highest recorded single-season batting average in <a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Minor_League_Baseball" title=3D"Minor League Basebal=
l">Minor League Baseball</a> is .462, accomplished by <a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gary_Redus" title=3D"Gary Redus">Gary Redus</a> in 1978=
, when he played for the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billings_=
Mustangs" title=3D"Billings Mustangs">Billings Mustangs</a>,<sup id=3D"cite=
_ref-38" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batti=
ng_average_(baseball)#cite_note-38"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>37=
<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-39" clas=
s=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batting_average_(b=
aseball)#cite_note-39"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>38<span class=
=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> an affiliate of the <a href=3D"https:/=
/en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cincinnati_Reds" title=3D"Cincinnati Reds">Cincinnat=
i Reds</a> in the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rookie_Advanced"=
 class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Rookie Advanced">Rookie Advanced</a>-level =
<a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pioneer_League_(baseball)" title=
=3D"Pioneer League (baseball)">Pioneer League</a>. Redus was 117-for-253 in=
 68 games,<sup id=3D"cite_ref-40" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en=
.wikipedia.org/wiki/Batting_average_(baseball)#cite_note-40"><span class=3D=
"cite-bracket">[</span>39<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup> as=
 the Pioneer League only plays from June to early September. Redus went on =
to play in MLB from 1982 through 1994, batting .252 during his MLB career.<=
sup id=3D"cite_ref-41" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.=
org/wiki/Batting_average_(baseball)#cite_note-41"><span class=3D"cite-brack=
et">[</span>40<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"Nippon_Professional_Basebal=
